      "role": "user",
      "content": "I just found out the data was all wrong. Ten years. Everything I've published, every lecture, every late night in the lab... it was all built on a single calculation error. It wasn't just a mistake, it was a delusion. I'm not a scientist, I'm just a fraud. There's nothing left of me.",
